title: Health Zingo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Indian, Organic, Fast food, Salad bar, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out
description: Vegetarian restaurant with vegan options. Serves organic juices, including wheatgrass. Also serves evening snacks, lunch and dinner combo and more. No fried foods. Uses cold pressed olive or safflower oil, multi grain breads and slow cooking and juicing to preserve nutrients. Located below Apollo Pharmacy.
